t4.Player

Class Player

  • java.lang.Object
    • t4.Player.Player
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Player>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BasicAI, Human, NewAI, RandomAI

    public abstract class Player
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Player>
    A Player represents a participant in the t4 game. Each Player has a name and an identifying piece that they'll play with.
    Author:
    Teddy
